Package com.six.timapi.constants

Enum Class KernelType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<KernelType>
com.six.timapi.constants.KernelType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<KernelType>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum KernelType extends Enum<KernelType>

Enumeration that specifies the type of kernel.

This field is used as attribute of the <sixml:KernelVersion> tag to specify the type of the kernel accoring to EMV.

The following values are valid:

Specification: retail.
